                        in <placeName key="#Churches">Ferignano</placeName>, <orgName>sancti
                            Comitii</orgName> iuxta <placeName ref="#places/556"
                        >Cicinam</placeName>. <orgName>Ecclesiam in vallis sancti
                            Christofori</orgName> in <placeName>Tabiano</placeName>, <orgName>sancti
